column10: Workflow initialized with News Fetcher problem description.
Invoked client agent for problem definition.
Provided goals
Advanced to requirements phase and invoked system_analyst.
Invoked system_analyst for requirements gathering.
Received answers to two clarification questions.
Created requirements.md with problem summary
Advanced to requirements review and invoked system_analyst_reviewer.
Invoked system_analyst_reviewer to review requirements.md.
Approved requirements.md; no required changes.
Advanced to architecture phase and invoked architect; created to_architect.md.
Invoked architect to create architect.md.
Created architect.md with system components
Advanced to architecture review and invoked architect_reviewer.
Invoked architect_reviewer to review architect.md.
Approved architect.md and created to_development.md.
Advanced to development phase and invoked devops.
Invoked devops to prepare runtime scaffolding.
Created README.md with run steps and env var instructions.
Invoked backend to implement FastAPI service.
Started backend implementation.
Implemented FastAPI backend with POST /news/fetch
Invoked frontend to implement React app.
Started frontend implementation.
Implemented React TypeScript frontend with category input
Advanced to testing phase and invoked tester.
Started testing phase.
Created test_report.md with backend and E2E test results; validated acceptance criteria.
Advanced to security review and invoked security agent.
Started security review of all artifacts.
Completed security review; no high/critical issues found; approved for delivery.
Advanced to delivery phase; preparing client report.
Completed News Fetcher workflow; delivered client_report.md.
Started comprehensive end-to-end integration testing.
Completed comprehensive end-to-end integration testing; all 11 tests passed; system ready for user testing.
Added dummy data functionality for demo/testing without API key.
